'''''Xucphra Rose''''' was one of three [[Bacta Tanker]]s hijacked by [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] during the [[Ambush of the bacta tankers]] from a small convoy escorted by the [[Victory II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Victory II''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Corrupter/Legends|''Corrupter'']]. After having surrendered, the ship accepted to carry its [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] to [[Halanit]]. During this trip, it was escorted by [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]], [[Ooryl Qrygg]] and two [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] [[Chir'daki]] starfighters.

The ship was captained by [[Bors Kenlin]].

